Welcome to Dasset


Dasset™ | algobet Labs © 2017


Know-how to Read




Dasset
 is not just a combined abbr. of "digital asset", but also an omni format in the digital asset world.


Dasset™
 is an unregistered brand for this digital asset system. The dictionary is available at 
http://dasset.trade
.




How to Test (for Developers)




Run a private blockchain, e.g., 
ethereum
, etc.


Run a content repo, e.g., 
ipfs
, etc.


Checkout the source code from 
http://...
 and configure the environment, e.g., 
nodejs
, 
meteor
, etc. Checklist available at 
http://dasset.trade/test/...


Test the project step by step as guided in the 
./README.md
.




How to Join (for Users)




Visit 
http://dasset.trade
 and register your domain.


Download mobile apps 
Dasset™ Go
(iOS) or 
Dasset™ OTG
(android).




Have A Great Day!
